						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">Quietust wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">Interestingly enough, ExRAM, while in mode 1, can only be written (via $5C00-$5FFF) <strong>while rendering</strong> - if you try to write during VBLANK (or while rendering is disabled), the data won't make it through properly.</div>
